import { CATEGORIES_TOP } from "../lib/categories";
---

<Base
  title="Cosmetic Surgery in Houston, TX | The Oaks Plastic Surgery"
  description="Cosmetic Surgery in Houston, TX at The Oaks Plastic Surgery. Board-certified plastic surgeons offering personalized care."
  headerTitle="Cosmetic Surgery in Houston, TX"
  headerImage="/img/mom-hero.jpg"
  headerMarginBottom={60}
  canonical="https://theoaksplasticsurgery.com/cosmetic-surgery-houston"
>
<section class="mb-0">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
                            <p class="wow fadeInUp lead text-center">
                                TOPS Houston provides high-end, luxury care for your cosmetic surgeries and procedures. You’ll be treated with highly personalized care in a luxury facility that makes your cosmetic procedure feel more like a trip to the spa. More importantly, you’ll be working with some of Houston’s leading cosmetic surgeons. As plastic surgeons, <a href="/drdanielleandry">Dr. Andry</a> and <a href="/nandi-wijay-houston">Dr. Wijay</a> spent years training in the latest cosmetic plastic surgery techniques. Drs. Andry and Wijay have been focused on cosmetic surgery from the beginning of their careers in medicine.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="mb-0 pb-240">
                <div class="container-fluid">
                    
                </div>
            </section>            
            <section class="text-section pb-240">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h2 class="wow fadeInUp center text-center">Our Most Popular Cosmetic Surgeries for the Neck & Above</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-jarallax-element="-150" class="text-section-box"></div>
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row text-row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/houston-facelift">Facelift</a></h3>
                                <p>
                                    Correct the more obvious signs of aging with one of the most common cosmetic surgeries in Houston. “Facelift” is a broad term that covers a variety of procedures to lift the skin and underlying tissues of the face, providing a more youthful look.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    At TOPS Houston, our techniques aim to offer a natural, rejuvenated look while avoiding methods that create overly-tightened skin.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/houston-necklift">Neck lift</a></h3>
                                <p>
                                    “Neck lift” refers to a variety of cosmetic procedures designed to give a firm, smooth appearance to the neck. Many of our Houston patients seek neck lifts to correct signs of aging, but neck lifts are also performed to reduce the appearance of double chins or add definition to poorly defined chins and jawlines.
                                </p>
                            </div>                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/houston-nose-jobs">Nose Job (Rhinoplasty)</a></h3>
                                <p class="align-content-end">
                                    As surgeons who perform rhinoplasty for all ethnicities, Dr. Andry and Dr. Wijay are skilled at offering any patient a restructured nose that suits their face, looks natural, and blends seamlessly with their other features. In addition to the aesthetic benefits of rhinoplasty, this cosmetic surgery may also provide an improvement to the functionality of a patient’s nose and sinuses if the patient has suffered from a deviated septum or other nasal passage issue.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/facial-fat-grafting-houston">Fat Grafting to the Face</a></h3>
                                <p class="align-content-end">
                                    A cutting edge cosmetic surgery technique, fat grafting to the face involves removing fat from the body through liposuction, processing it through specialized techniques, and injecting it into the face for a fuller, more youthful look. Because your own body will create new blood-flow to the fat, the results typically last longer than those of traditional fillers.
                                </p>
                            </div>                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="text-section pb-240">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h2 class="wow fadeInUp center text-center">Our Most Popular Cosmetic Surgeries for the Upper Body</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-jarallax-element="-150" class="text-section-box"></div>
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row text-row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/breast-augmentation-houston">Breast Augmentation</a></h3>
                                <p>
                                    By far one of our most common cosmetic surgeries, breast augmentation at TOPS Houston can improve the size, shape, and symmetry of your breasts. Dr. Andry and Dr. Wijay take an individualized approach to breast implant surgery, ensuring that you receive the results you want through personalized care. From the size of your implants to the placement of your incisions, you’ll work with your doctor to choose every detail of your breast augmentation.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/breast-lift-surgery-houston">Breast Lift (Mastopexy)</a></h3>
                                <p>
                                    Breast lifts are often performed along with other cosmetic procedures like breast augmentation or “mommy makeovers,” but many of our Houston patients also seek mastopexy as a standalone cosmetic surgery. If you’ve experienced sagging or deflation of the breasts due to pregnancy, nursing, or aging, a breast lift will restore youthful perkiness to your breasts.
                                </p>
                            </div>                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/breast-reduction-houston">Breast Reduction</a></h3>
                                <p class="align-content-end">
                                    While breast reductions can improve the overall appearance of your breasts, for many patients, reduction is more than a cosmetic surgery. Reductions can dramatically improve symptoms of back pain, neck pain, and poor posture. TOPS Houston cosmetic surgeons can perform <a href="/gynecomastia-houston">male breast reductions</a> for men who suffer from gynecomastia.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/houston-tummy-tucks">Tummy Tuck</a></h3>
                                <p class="align-content-end">
                                    Tummy tucks focus on removing excess fat and skin around the stomach area. Tummy tucks also help repair the separation of the abdominal muscles (abs or six pack) after pregnancy or massive weight loss.
                                </p>
                            </div>                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="text-section pb-240">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h2 class="wow fadeInUp center text-center">Our Most Popular Cosmetic Surgeries for the Lower Body</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-jarallax-element="-150" class="text-section-box"></div>
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row text-row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/butt-lift-houston">Brazilian Butt Lift</a></h3>
                                <p>
                                    A Brazilian butt lift is a cosmetic procedure that involves harvesting fat from another area of the body through liposuction and transferring it to the buttocks and hips for a fuller, curvier figure. Because fat is usually transferred from the midsection, Brazilian butt lifts will also help accentuate your waistline, helping to create an ideal hourglass shape.
                                </p>
                            </div>                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/lipectomy-houston">Lower Body Lift (Lipectomy)</a></h3>
                                <p class="align-content-end">
                                    Lipectomies help improve the appearance of the hips, buttocks, and saddle bag areas by removing excess skin. This procedure is most often sought after by those who have achieved massive weight loss and is often performed with other cosmetic surgeries like tummy tucks.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="text-section pb-240">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h2 class="wow fadeInUp center text-center">Our Most Popular All-in-One Solutions and Lifts</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-jarallax-element="-150" class="text-section-box"></div>
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row text-row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/mommy-makeover-houston">Mommy Makeover</a></h3>
                                <p>
                                    Many mothers experience a massive toll to the body after pregnancy and childbirth and struggle to feel like themselves again even after they’ve lost most of their pregnancy weight. Mommy makeovers include multiple cosmetic surgeries and procedures designed to restore and improve your postpartum body. The most common procedures performed during a mommy makeover are tummy tucks, breast lifts, breast augmentation and vaginal rejuvenations.
                                </p>
                            </div>                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/contact-us">Massive Weight Loss</a></h3>
                                <p class="align-content-end">
                                    Lipectomies help improve the appearance of the hips, buttocks, and saddle bag areas by removing excess skin. This procedure is most often sought after by those who have achieved massive weight loss and is often performed with other cosmetic surgeries like tummy tucks.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="text-section pb-240">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h2 class="wow fadeInUp center text-center">Our Most Popular Non-surgical Cosmetic Procedures</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-jarallax-element="-150" class="text-section-box"></div>
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row text-row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/fillers-houston">Filler Injections</a></h3>
                                <p>
                                    Injectable fillers are used to improve signs of aging in targeted areas of the face. The perfect solution for those who don’t want cosmetic surgery, fillers are a non-invasive way to combat fine lines, wrinkles, and deflated skin.
                                </p>
                            </div>                            
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/fillers-houston">Botox, Jeuveau, and Dysport</a></h3>
                                <p>
                                    Injectable fillers are used to improve signs of aging in targeted areas of the face. The perfect solution for those who don’t want cosmetic surgery, fillers are a non-invasive way to combat fine lines, wrinkles, and deflated skin.
                                </p>
                            </div>                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 pt-lg-5">
                            <div class="text-section-block">
                                <h3><a href="/microneedling-houston">Microneedling with PRP</a></h3>
                                <p class="align-content-end">
                                    Microneedling with PRP (Platelet rich plasma) facials get their name because they use your own blood to add youthfulness to your face. This relatively new procedure is rapidly growing in popularity as a way to achieve natural rejuvenation of the skin.	
                                </p>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="text-section pb-240">
